OL,3,CFamily 'torn apart' as father and son
OL,4,Ckilled in crash named
OL,6,FThe family of a father and son who
OL,7,Fdied in a crash in South Tyneside say
OL,8,Ftheir world has been "completely torn
OL,9,Fapart".
OL,11,FPeter Webb, 40, and his 12-year-old
OL,12,Fson Ben, both from South Shields, were
OL,13,Fkilled when the white Skoda Octavia
OL,14,Fthey were travelling in left John Reid
OL,15,FRoad near the New Mill Inn at around
OL,16,F8.55pm on Saturday (30 September).
OL,18,FBoth were pronounced dead at the scene.
