OL,3,CFamily 'torn apart' as father and son
OL,4,Ckilled in crash named
OL,6,FIn a statement, Peter and Ben's family
OL,7,Fsaid: "Our world has been completely
OL,8,Ftorn apart. We have no words to
OL,9,Fdescribe how devastating this has been.
OL,11,F"We will however continue to stick
OL,12,Ftogether as one while we navigate a
OL,13,Fsituation we never believed we would
OL,14,Fbe in.
OL,16,F"Peter was a kind wonderful human who
OL,17,Fwould do anything for his family.
OL,19,F"Ben was the most incredible ray of
OL,20,Fsunshine with an unbelievable sense of
OL,21,Fhumour.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/5
