OL,6,F"They are together forever. Please
OL,7,Flook after our boy, until we meet
OL,8,Fagain."
OL,10,FThe family is receiving support from
OL,11,Fspecialist officers while
OL,12,Finvestigations into the collision
OL,13,Fcontinue.
OL,15,FSergeant Russell Surrey, who is
OL,16,Fleading Northumbria Police's
OL,17,Finvestigation into the crash, said:
OL,18,F"The sympathies of everyone here at
OL,19,FNorthumbria Police continue to be with
OL,20,FPeter and Ben's family.
