OL,6,F"We cannot begin to understand their
OL,7,Floss but are committed to do
OL,8,Feverything we can to provide any
OL,9,Fanswers to their loved ones at this
OL,10,Fawful time.
OL,12,F"I'd like to thank everyone who has
OL,13,Fbeen in touch so far with information.
OL,14,FYour support to our investigation is
OL,15,Falways appreciated.
OL,17,F"If you were in the area at the time
OL,18,Fand have any CCTV or dashcam footage
OL,19,Fwhich could assist our investigation,
OL,20,Fplease reach out to us as soon as
OL,21,Fyou're able to."
